msgid "Episode I: Escape the Living"
msgstr ""

#. [campaign]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/_main.cfg:63
msgid ""
"This is the tale of an age when the glory of Wesnoth was transformed into arrogance. The fugitive necromancer Gwiti Ha’atel is resolved to master the undead hordes and exact his revenge against all who have betrayed him. His journey soon leaves his own hands, morphing into an enormous wave of power...\n"
"\n"
"(Intermediate level, 8 scenarios.)"
msgstr ""

