msgid "Episode II: The Death March"
msgstr ""

#. [campaign]
#: The_Dark_Hordes/_main.cfg:79
msgid ""
"At last, the deadly forces of Gwiti begin their invasion against Wesnoth. As the shadows of his rule terrorize the Kingdom and its people, they turn to the elven enchantress Elynia for their last hope. Will it be the Light or the Darkness that stands in the end? No one who knows — except for only one.\n"
"\n"
"(Intermediate level, 6 scenarios.)"
